					<hr />
					<h2>Ways to reach us.</h2>
					<h3 class='h6'>Office</h3>
					<address>
						924 Hale <br />
						Brooksville
					</address>
					<p><a href='tel:+1-352-325-7688'>352-325-7688</a></p>
				</div>
				<div class='contact-section-column'>
					<p data-lg-reveal='fade' data-lg-reveal-delay='.25'>
						Interested in our services? Fill out our contact form or setup a chat with Matt. Heâ€™d love to talk
						with and see how Kelp can be of help.
					</p>
